Class AndCompositeTool

  • java.lang.Object

    CursorTool, MouseListener, MouseMotionListener, EventListener

    public class AndCompositeTool
extends CompositeTool
    Enables multiple CursorTools to operate at the same time. Events are passed to all CursorTools in sequence.
